data.description: Welcome to a stunning two-story residence boasting four bedrooms, two and a half baths, and a two-car attached garage! Upon entering this house, you'll be greeted with a tiled entrance, an office with double doors, a generously sized living area showcasing high ceilings and abundant natural light from the ample windows, a utility area, and a powder room. The kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, an island, a breakfast bar, and a breakfast nook right beside it. The main bedroom has an en-suite bathroom with dual sinks, a garden tub, separate shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. The upper floor accommodates a sizeable game room, three additional bedrooms, and another full bathroom. The fenced backyard is perfect for leisure, complete with a covered patio and a pathway leading to an expansive wooden deck. Situated in the meticulously planned community of Newport, this home offers easy access to I-90/Crosby Freeway and is a stone's throw away from Lake Houston!
